These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: writing, cooking
Job: electrician, scientist
1. Job:electrician is in an even position##4
2. Job:scientist == Hobby:cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | cooking | writing |
| Job     | scientist    | electrician   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: mirinda, juice
Sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. Sport:skateboarding is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:juice is on the left of Beverage:mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | juice | mirinda        |
| Sport      | skateboarding  | snowboarding |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: folk, trance
Nationality: chinese, australian
1. Nationality:chinese is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:trance is on the left of Music-Genre:folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | folk |
| Nationality   | chinese | australian |

